                    "type": "TextualBody",
                    "value": "<p rend=\"align(right)\"><placeName>New York</placeName>\n                                        <date>May 1st 1851</date>.</p>\n                              <p>Dr. Sir.</p>\n                              <p rend=\"indent(1)\">Have you on hand a set of the Pentateuch<lb/> of\n                                        the larger size (Octavo)â€”bound or unbound; and<lb/> if\n                                        bound, describe to me the same and its price; and<lb/> if\n                                        unbound the expense of binding the same, of<lb/> red, light\n                                        purple, or gray colour, with gilding of<lb/> the leaves in\n                                        the usual way; and also the article<lb/> used for binding,\n                                        morocco or cloth: with the ornamen-<lb/>tal part of the\n                                        binding's. Respectfully</p>\n                              <p rend=\"align(right)\"><persName role=\"author\">Washington\n                                                  Judah</persName>.</p>\n                              <p><addressee>Rev. Isaac Leeser</addressee>.</p>\n                              <p rend=\"indent(1)\">Direct your reply to \"<placeName>No 319 Henry\n                                                  street</placeName>\"</p>"
